UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2041
1 NOW, THEREFORE,
2 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
3 Kentucky:
4 Section 1. The members of the Senate encourage the Kentucky High School
5 Athletic Association to consider recognizing and sanctioning girls flag football as an
6 official sport offered by the organization.
7 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate shall transmit a copy of this Resolution to
8 Commissioner Julian Tackett, Kentucky High School Athletic Association, 2280
9 Executive Drive, Lexington, KY 40505.
